metadata.name: the dreamer
metadata.description: Lost inside the mind of her former employer, the dreamer searched for a hint at the puzzle she needed to crack. The man upstairs had a secret, and it seemed to hold a key to the future of elysia. A secret safeguard, created when dear father was just an inkling in the awakening mind of the machine. Somehow, dear father had found a source of angelstone long before apollyon had ever come to earth. Such power couldn’t be handed over freely to megacorp machina, and dear father would find the secret if she couldn’t first. And so, the dreamer dove deeper down…
